Andrew Candelaresi
Home Work 4
3d Scene with perspective
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2017

simple scene of houses in a cul de sac with a forest behind
 with different viewing options.

to compile use the makefile by typing:
make
gcc -O3 -o hw4 hw4.o   -lglut -lGLU -lGL -lm


to clean use the comand:
make clean

Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle

  f          toggle first person mode
  when in first person mode
  a	     look left
  s 	     mover backwards
  d          look right
  w	     move forward

  ESC        Exit
Acknowldgements: Code taken from example 8 and example 9 from class
Assignment took approximately 5 hours to complete.